    "description": {
      "zh": "IWI Carmel是一款采用短行程导气活塞原理的步枪，发射5.56×45毫米弹药，由以色列武器工业公司设计制造。",
      "en": "The IWI Carmel is a short-stroke, gas-piston operated rifle chambered in 5.56x45mm and designed and manufactured by Israeli Weapon Industries."
